<br />with landmass,</p>
        <p begin="00:01:59.450" end="00:02:02.310" tts:direction="ltr">I might use something called a tile map.</p>
        <p begin="00:02:02.310" end="00:02:04.710" tts:direction="ltr">This is an opportunity where you'll use</p>
        <p begin="00:02:04.710" end="00:02:08.330" tts:direction="ltr">a shape to create a shape of the United
<br />States.</p>
        <p begin="00:02:08.330" end="00:02:11.270" tts:direction="ltr">Now Alaska is much smaller.</p>
        <p begin="00:02:11.270" end="00:02:13.130" tts:direction="ltr">They're all the same size.</p>
        <p begin="00:02:13.130" end="00:02:15.590" tts:direction="ltr">That's in Hawaii is much smaller too.</p>
        <p begin="00:02:15.590" end="00:02:17.650" tts:direction="ltr">What that can do though is that can really</p>
