        <p begin="00:02:49.760" end="00:02:51.880" tts:direction="ltr">If you want to take a moment and fill</p>
        <p begin="00:02:51.880" end="00:02:56.040" tts:direction="ltr">in the great state of Utah on your x map,</p>
        <p begin="00:02:56.040" end="00:02:58.160" tts:direction="ltr">that's that star that I have right there.</p>
        <p begin="00:02:58.160" end="00:02:59.985" tts:direction="ltr">That's where Utah would be placed.</p>
        <p begin="00:02:59.985" end="00:03:04.190" tts:direction="ltr">Okay. Let's talk about shape.</p>
        <p begin="00:03:04.190" end="00:03:07.230" tts:direction="ltr">Here I've got my lovely circles,</p>
        <p begin="00:03:07.230" end="00:03:09.650" tts:direction="ltr">and I have one x.</p>
        <p begin="00:03:09.650" end="00:03:14.310" tts:direction="ltr">Now, of course, you cannot help but see
<br />the difference,</p>
        <p begin="00:03:14.310" end="00:03:17.170" tts:direction="ltr">and that will go to our idea of contrast.</p>
        <p begin="00:03:17.170" end="00:03:21.090" tts:direction="ltr">Whenever I have something that's different
<br />that I'm breaking the pattern,</p>
        <p begin="00:03:21.090" end="00:03:25.310" tts:direction="ltr">humans will go first to the broken pattern
<br />to the difference.</p>
        <p begin="00:03:25.310" end="00:03:28.090" tts:direction="ltr">That's just part of our super scales as
<br />humans.</p>
        <p begin="00:03:28.090" end="00:03:31.990" tts:direction="ltr">I'm going to see the x in a of circles.</p>
        <p begin="00:03:31.990" end="00:03:38.110" tts:direction="ltr">If I have all of these plots here on the
<br />scatter plot for fruit types,</p>
        <p begin="00:03:38.110" end="00:03:40.690" tts:direction="ltr">sales versus profit, You can see</p>
        <p begin="00:03:40.690" end="00:03:43.910" tts:direction="ltr">here that I am looking at these different
<br />shapes.</p>
        <p begin="00:03:43.910" end="00:03:46.110" tts:direction="ltr">They're all different and</p>
        <p begin="00:03:46.110" end="00:03:49.370" tts:direction="ltr">they're all about the same size, but
<br />they're contrasting.</p>
        <p begin="00:03:49.370" end="00:03:53.090" tts:direction="ltr">Now if I wanted to have one of those
