        <p begin="00:03:53.090" end="00:03:55.670" tts:direction="ltr">maybe I wanted to focus on the apples,</p>
        <p begin="00:03:55.670" end="00:04:00.330" tts:direction="ltr">I could leave that as a circle and then
<br />change all the rest to squares.</p>
        <p begin="00:04:00.330" end="00:04:03.030" tts:direction="ltr">I'm using that same principle I had here,</p>
        <p begin="00:04:03.030" end="00:04:09.220" tts:direction="ltr">but now I'm going to pull out the apples
