        <p begin="00:04:16.970" end="00:04:19.050" tts:direction="ltr">and then I can get rid of the legend.</p>
        <p begin="00:04:19.050" end="00:04:21.110" tts:direction="ltr">Do you see how I have no legend here?</p>
        <p begin="00:04:21.110" end="00:04:26.450" tts:direction="ltr">I'm able to remove that because now you
