        <p begin="00:04:43.530" end="00:04:44.890" tts:direction="ltr">I highly recommend there's</p>
        <p begin="00:04:44.890" end="00:04:48.230" tts:direction="ltr">so many inspiring dashboards and</p>
        <p begin="00:04:48.230" end="00:04:51.890" tts:direction="ltr">you might even be able to find something
